description: Try our easy to follow Macadamia & Coconut Muffins recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Macadamia & Coconut Muffins Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Divide among muffin holes. Top with coconut. Bake for 20 minutes or until a skewer inserted into centre comes out clean. Serve warm or at room temperature.
